        "content": [
          "POSITION \u2014 where these clusters go:",
          "",
          "BEFORE conjugated verbs:",
          "",
          "   Me lo d\u00e0.     = He gives it to me.",
          "   Glielo mando. = I send it to him.",
          "   Gliene parlo. = I tell him of it.",
          "",
          "ATTACHED to infinitives, imperatives,",
