          "",
          "chi se ne frega? = chin flicked outward.",
          "   Dismissal. Colloquial, not rude.",
          "",
          "che furbo!       = index taps temple.",
          "   'Clever!' \u2014 or 'you can't fool me.'",
          "",
          "cornuto!         = index + pinky out.",
          "   Insult of betrayal. Use with caution.",
